1
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,000
Let Ji Bai

2
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:22,400
at least escort you to meet your friends.

3
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:24,039
It's settled.

4
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:26,370
Go with Ruyan to prepare the medicine.

5
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,200
Sorry to trouble you.

6
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:31,400
Yes, Your Highness.

7
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,200
You can run, but you can't hide forever.

8
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:53,720
When the time comes, the entire Zhenbei Prince's Mansion won't escape.

9
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,520
Miss Ji.

10
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,160
Please lead the way.

11
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,360
This is the Mansion's private pharmacy.

12
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,240
His Highness also instructed,

13
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,920
that if you see any herbs you like,

14
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:23,320
please take them. Don't stand on ceremony.

15
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,960
Then I won't disturb you any longer, Miss.

16
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,400
If you have any orders,

17
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,040
just call out.

18
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,300
I'll be right outside.

19
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,250
Here.

20
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,440
I need to prepare some more medicine.

21
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,240
Give this to the Prince of Zhenbei.

22
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,320
Tell him to just do as I said before.

23
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:00,920
Yes, sir.

24
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,280
Miss,

25
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,940
it's late and unsafe at night.

26
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,600
Whatever you need to do, please wait until tomorrow.

27
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,360
The Prince has ordered

28
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,400
that you are not allowed to leave for now.

29
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:11,920
Miss.

30
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,160
We are merely acting on orders.

31
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,620
Please try to understand.

32
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,660
Forgive me.

33
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,060
Go report to the Prince immediately.

34
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,320
Your Highness.

35
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,800
Should we send someone to bring back the Princess Consort?

36
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,000
Enough.

37
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,440
Since she left in such a hurry,

38
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,240
she must have urgent business.

39
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,210
I just hope those people didn't discover her.

40
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,680
As long as she encounters no danger, it is fine.

41
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,840
Your Highness, based on the scent trail Miss Ji left,

42
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,120
I have confirmed it is the Heir.

43
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,760
But then,

44
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,360
your men lost him.

45
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,170
Yes, Your Highness.

46
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,920
But I traced the direction the Heir went.

47
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,400
It seems to be Sitai Town.

48
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,360
Your Highness,

49
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,640
should we send someone

50
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,520
to track down the Heir?

51
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:20,760
No.

52
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,840
We shouldn't alert the enemy right now.

53
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:28,280
Suppress the news that the Heir and Princess Consort have left the manor.

54
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,760
Also, strengthen the manor's security.

55
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,160
And...

56
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:36,320
you must inform me of any news from the Capital immediately.

57
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:39,490
Yes, Your Highness. I will attend to it immediately.

58
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,960
I fear he already suspects something

59
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,680
and has gone to investigate the truth himself.

60
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,640
It seems

61
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,840
I must go to the Capital

62
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:02,000
to ascertain the new Emperor's stance

63
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:06,640
regarding the incident from years ago.

64
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,720
Sir,

65
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,200
do you know where Baishitong is?

66
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,400
Baishitong?

67
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,240
Yes.

68
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,320
They are also known as the Inquirers.

69
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,960
They appear often in storybooks.

70
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,240
They know everything.

71
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,720
This Know-It-All

72
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,840
is a legend.

73
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,640
But finding him

74
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,040
won't be easy.

75
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,720
As long as I find him,

76
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,500
I'll make it worth your while.

77
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,880
The Know-It-All

78
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,680
is at the grocery market in the east of town,

79
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,340
in the most conspicuous spot.

80
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,080
Thanks.

81
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,320
What a fool.

82
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,640
Sir,

83
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,560
do you know where Baishitong is?

84
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,200
It's been desolate for years.

85
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,610
There is no Baishitong.

86
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,970
But there is 'passing gas'.

87
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,440
Move aside.

88
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,200
That damn swindler.

89
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,880
He took all my money.

90
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,200
When I find you,

91
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,480
I won't spare you.

92
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,840
This wine smells good.

93
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,400
Li Si will love it.

94
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,880
Li Si.

95
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,560
Not bad, Li Si.

96
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,440
Just sit with your back to the door.

97
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,840
Your silhouette is enough to pass for real.

98
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,600
Your Highness,

99
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,000
let's switch back.

100
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,130
You can usually sneak out of the manor,

101
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,799
only because the Prince turns a blind eye.

102
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:39,960
Now even the dog hole is guarded.

103
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,440
Don't worry.

104
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,400
I have a plan.

105
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,420
My father won't make things hard for you.

106
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,440
Drink some wine to calm your nerves.

107
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,320
I dare not. I dare not.

108
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,040
How can I let you pour wine for me?

109
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:58,420
This is fine tribute wine for the palace.

110
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,840
Then I shall accept.

111
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,100
Thank you for the reward, Your Highness.

112
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,160
Don't drink!

113
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:24,520
Li Si!

114
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:29,220
Those footsteps don't belong to anyone from the manor.

115
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,000
Your Highness.

116
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,440
Brother Li.

117
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,760
The one who killed you

118
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,970
must be connected to what I'm investigating.

119
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,320
I will avenge you.

120
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:01,770
Shopkeeper.

121
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:06,320
No wine, just water. Thanks.

122
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,640
It's her.

123
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,360
Is she here to take me back to the manor?

124
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,440
But Father shouldn't have sent her.

125
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:26,560
Your hand might have a snakehead sore.

126
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,040
You should go to a clinic.

127
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:28,770
This girl...

128
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,260
Are you cursing me?

129
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,440
Go away.

130
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,440
No, wait.

131
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:35,360
If your hand is starting to hurt

132
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,800
but isn't swollen yet,

133
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,640
you can soak it in hot salt water

134
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,640
for the time it takes to drink a cup of tea.

135
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,960
The pain will go away.

136
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:44,000
Just go.

137
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,160
Let's go.

138
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:48,930
Let's head up the mountain.

139
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:56,080
That little brat is a jinx.

140
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,640
Looks like she went up the mountain.

141
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,620
She dares to go up the mountain alone.

142
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,920
She'll be food for the beasts.

143
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,880
If that girl didn't truly care,

144
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,920
she wouldn't have wasted her breath.

145
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:14,120
Cursing her like that

146
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:16,300
shows you don't recognize kindness.

147
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,560
She is just a girl.

148
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,960
What does she know about medicine?

149
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,360
It is all nonsense.

150
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,400
If you don't believe her,

151
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:23,040
just turn a deaf ear.

152
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,800
But if she is right,

153
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,040
and something happens to your finger,

154
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:29,440
don't regret ignoring her advice.

155
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:31,880
Go up the mountain.

156
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,840
As the Prime Minister's daughter,

157
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:36,520
why does she seem so familiar with this place?

158
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,680
That's the person I saw at the Prince's Manor.

159
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,280
They don't look friendly.

160
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,600
Are they here to capture me?

161
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,800
But the Prince doesn't seem like that kind of person.

162
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:55,660
Isn't this the Princess Consort?

163
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:59,520
It seems the Heir really has come to Sitai Town.

164
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,600
You've got the wrong person.

165
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,200
Where is Xiao Heyan?

166
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,170
I don't know him.

167
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,760
It seems, Princess Consort,

168
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,840
you want to do this the hard way.

169
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:17,500
She really isn't one of the Prince's people.

170
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,880
Princess Consort.

171
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,520
With your skills,

172
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,640
you can barely hold out for a while.

173
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,240
But as time passes,

174
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,840
your stamina will fail you.

175
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:54,840
Why not just surrender

176
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,160
and tell me where the Heir is?

177
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,600
I shouldn't have followed her.

178
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,730
What if this is an ambush set by Father?

179
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:08,720
But what if she runs into danger alone?

180
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,860
The smell of blood.

181
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:26,160
You.

182
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,360
It really is you.

183
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,130
Chen, Luo, Deng.

184
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,080
Yi, Yi, Nan.

185
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,560
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

186
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,000
Guo, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

187
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,130
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

188
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:36,560
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

189
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,560
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

190
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:41,920
Pan, Xiu, Long.

191
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,520
Pan, Xiu, Long.

192
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,440
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

193
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:42,720
Pan, Xiu, Long.
